OL,3,CPolice officer filmed 'stamping on
OL,4,Cman's head' at airport
OL,6,FA police force has defended the
OL,7,Factions of an officer caught on camera
OL,8,Fkicking a man before stamping on his
OL,9,Fhead while he was on the floor.
OL,11,FFootage has been widely circulated on
OL,12,Fsocial media of an incident at
OL,13,FManchester Airport on Wednesday 24
OL,14,FJuly.
OL,16,FThe footage, which lasts for more than
OL,17,F40 seconds, shows a fire arm officer
OL,18,Fkicking and stamping on a man's head.
