OL,3,CPolice officer filmed 'stamping on
OL,4,Cman's head' at airport
OL,6,FIt later shows the same officer, who
OL,7,Fwas accompanied by two other officers,
OL,8,Farmed with tasers, striking another
OL,9,Fman on the back of his head.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,12,Fconfirmed a female police officer
OL,13,Fsustained a broken nose as three
OL,14,Fofficers were subject to a "violent
OL,15,Fassault" in the incident at Terminal
OL,16,F2, in the run up to the footage being
OL,17,Ftaken.
OL,19,FIt also said there had been a risk of
OL,20,Fthe armed officers' "firearms being
OL,21,Ftaken".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
