OL,3,CPolice officer filmed 'stamping on
OL,4,Cman's head' at airport
OL,6,FIn the footage a male officer can be
OL,7,Fseen aiming a taser at a man as he is
OL,8,Flying on the ground.
OL,10,FOnlookers can then be heard shouting
OL,11,Fbefore the officer kicks and stamps on
OL,12,Fthe man's head.
OL,14,FA person is heard yelling "move back",
OL,15,Fbefore a female officer then appears
OL,16,Fto turn her taser and aim it at other
OL,17,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
