OL,3,CPolice officer filmed 'stamping on
OL,4,Cman's head' at airport
OL,6,F"Whilst attempting to arrest one of
OL,7,Fthe suspects of the earlier
OL,8,Faltercation, three officers were
OL,9,Fsubject to violent assault, where they
OL,10,Fwere punched to the ground.
OL,12,F"A female officer suffered a broken
OL,13,Fnose and all three were taken to
OL,14,Fhospital for treatment.
OL,16,F"As the attending officers were
OL,17,Ffirearms officers there was a clear
OL,18,Frisk during this assault of their
OL,19,Ffirearms being taken from them"
